## 3. Editing Constraints

### index.html
- MUST remain a single self-contained file — no external CSS/JS files
- All CSS in one `<style>` block, all JS in one `<script>` block
- Only external dependencies: Google Fonts (Plus Jakarta Sans + Inter), Font Awesome 6 CDN
- Update `<meta name="version">` and `<meta name="date">` on every edit
- After every change: update `CHANGELOG.md` and `docs/manifest.json` version_history

### Document Management
- `CHANGELOG.md` uses [Keep a Changelog](https://keepachangelog.com/) format with semver
- `docs/manifest.json` is the machine-readable registry — keep `current_version` and `version_history` in sync
- `docs/STATUS.md` is the human dashboard — update file map and version table after structural changes

