## 7. Industry Reference — AI in Cheese QC

### Eberle × Gebr. Baldauf Case Study
- **Source:** [MVTec](https://www.mvtec.com/), [RoboticsTomorrow](https://www.roboticstomorrow.com/), [Drives&Controls](https://drivesncontrols.com/)
- **What:** Mobile robot with 4K cameras + MVTec HALCON deep learning
- **Challenge:** Natural variability — every wheel looks different
- **Solution:** Deep learning trained on cheese surface data to distinguish true defects from natural rind variation
- **Results:** 100% inspection rate, 24/7 autonomous operation, reduced waste, full digital traceability
- **Relevance:** Exact same technology applicable to Džiugas ripening process

