## 8. Tone & Language Rules

- Board-presentation grade: **formal, respectful, consultative**
- Heritage-first: AI serves tradition, never replaces it
- NEVER use: "profit engine", "kill", "disrupt", "crush", "dominate"
- NEVER fabricate quotes attributed to Džiugas/ŽP leadership
- All statistics must be sourced or clearly marked as projections
- Strategic terminology: **Core / Strategic / Explore** (never MARRY/KISS/KILL)
- The Džiugas Principle statement is labeled "Design philosophy" — not a client quote

